    "Accuracy = (T P + T N)/(T P + T N + F P + F N) Precision = TP/(TP + FP)Recall = TP/(TP + FN)(1)In this research, the model's performance was evaluated using a subjective assessment approach, wherein manually created images and frames depicting emotions were compared individually.",
